      • getPermLevel

        @JsonProperty
public java.lang.Integer getPermLevel()
        Returns an integer from 0 to 2 inclusive that represents the permissions of that page. A permlevel of 0 means that this wiki page is following the default subreddit permissions, 1 means that on approved wiki contributors for this page may edit, and 2 means only mods may edit and view.
        Returns:
        An integer from 0 to 2 inclusive
